Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.70,0:00:04.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.43,0:00:06.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Comment: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:06.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:07.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.10,0:00:12.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:12.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent the night here last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:15.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:17.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.11,0:00:19.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring all this from your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:20.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.82,0:00:24.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're more suited to travel than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:25.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:28.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.39,0:00:30.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:30.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried about you since you didn't come yesterday.
Comment: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:33.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About you, uncessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:36.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad I made that wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:37.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.27,0:00:37.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.27,0:00:42.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wished upon the stardust that you would come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.17,0:00:43.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.67,0:00:43.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's have breakfast, breakfast!
Comment: 0,0:00:43.67,0:00:45.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Awkward double breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:47.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.51,0:00:47.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna eat too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.51,0:00:49.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't be such a pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:51.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:51.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:52.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:25.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you wait for me this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:26.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:29.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, I had something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:30.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:32.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:38.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still having those dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:38.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:42.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, it was about a forest at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:45.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking with someone in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:46.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:46.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:50.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but there was someone beside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:53.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked her what an ocean was.
Comment: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:54.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gender: He or she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:57.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, she told me many things about the ocean.
Comment: 0,0:02:57.97,0:02:57.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: many things -> lots
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:03:00.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was really fun just talking to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:05.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so fun that I wanted to wrap her words up and keep them forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:09.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was that fun, then sleep forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.28,0:03:10.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gao...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:12.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Comment: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:15.95,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 6
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:20.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A fan, a fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:22.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:23.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:25.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:25.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:29.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How did your puppet shows go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:32.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Well... Not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:32.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:36.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito Kunisaki, you good-for-nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:39.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:42.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:42.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who eats for free shouldn't talk so conceitedly!
Comment: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:42.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Awkward phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:46.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing, eating and sleeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:49.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in a really enviable position.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.26,0:03:53.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, I dreamt of my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:55.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:04:00.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, we would often sit here together and watch the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a dream of those times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:02.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:10.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In each and every star, there is a god watching over us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:14.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They also purify the hearts of those who watch the stars.
Comment: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:15.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: hearts -> souls
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:20.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A short time after that, he left home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:26.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After my younger sister died, my parents started to fight.
Comment: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:26.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: fight -> quarrel
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:28.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:33.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He married another woman in a faraway town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:38.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When he left, he gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:43.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you have to work now?
Comment: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:43.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: + go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:44.01,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:49.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Minagi has run away from home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:50.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:51.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you try to hide it from me, I can tell, because I'm her best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:56.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Things can't remain like this after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:05:00.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi has to wake up from her dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:03.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:05.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go home now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.37,0:05:07.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:07.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:08.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko pika.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:11.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:12.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:14.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:17.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:21.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry to have bothered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:25.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:25.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need anything, don't hesitate to stop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:34.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's starting to remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:38.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:38.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she lost something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:40.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She came here just because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:45.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just told her that she would eventually remember when she found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:49.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is up to Minagi-san's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:03.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:06.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:09.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to leave town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:10.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:14.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've stayed too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:15.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's time for me to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:18.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I... see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:20.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come with me, Tohno?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:21.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:27.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to show you the world;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:27.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the real world, not a dream world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The world...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:32.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go together to discover that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:39.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:41.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:47.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:48.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:52.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we go,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:52.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to say something to Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:54.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry; just follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:12.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:18.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.07,0:07:22.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru said that she doesn't want to see Minagi looking sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:23.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:27.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You must decide for yourself what you are going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:30.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, you really can come on a journey with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:33.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you along to wherever I end up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:35.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your choice.
Comment: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:35.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: The choice is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:40.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You, Minagi Tohno, must decide of your own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:51.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:17.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy?
Comment: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:17.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother or mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:17.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:53.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:04.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Comment: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:17.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother or mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:17.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The stars are amazing tonight too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:18.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:20.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Minagi is looking at the stars too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:23.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, probably with her mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:30.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:35.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's getting late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:37.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, I'll walk you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:40.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:42.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a home to return to.
Comment: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:42.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: I have a place to go back to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:43.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:48.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the sky, there's a really sad-looking girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:50.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:50.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:55.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl always just sees sad dreams and has nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:10:00.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't be happy, so all she can have is sad dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:03.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On her back, she has wounded feathers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:06.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,feathers with a really mysterious power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:12.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're packed with the memories of many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:19.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked for one of the plumes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:20.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because there was someone I wanted to comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:23.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I thought if that person became happy, then the girl in the sky would become happy too.
Comment: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:26.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a split?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:32.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People can't live without memories, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:37.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, they can't live on memories alone either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:40.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to wake from your dreams sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:45.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because dreams that you don't wake up from eventually become sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:49.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to return the feather.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:55.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to say goodbye to everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:55.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,'I dont want to say' or 'it's sad to say'
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:55.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but because I'm just a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:58.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because stars must disappear when the sun rises...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:00.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:06.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a fragment of a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:06.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My being here is just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:09.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know, it was a really fun dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:12.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:13.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:16.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The real Michiru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:21.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,wasn't allowed to be born into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:42.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I met Michiru for the first time at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:48.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every day, I went to the station to pick my father up, even after he had left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:52.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Father had already quit his job there,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:56.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but there was nothing else I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:12:01.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it then that your mother started calling you Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:01.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:07.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But as long as I was Michiru, Mother kept smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:13.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijiri told me it was around then that you stopped smiling as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:16.80,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:21.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was one summer afternoon after a rain storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:35.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt like I had seen her before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:40.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt that she was always nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:46.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:46.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:51.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... Minagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:56.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything started with my sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.91,0:12:58.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:02.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't wished for a little sister, no one would have had to dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:11.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I might even have to hurt Michiru,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:17.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but even then, I still want her to meet someone, someone very important.
Comment: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:17.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Koi's: I want to let someone very important catch at least one glimpse of her... this seems clumsy, but I'll let you decide. Also listen to the jap phrasing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:19.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:23.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan, hurry up, or we won't be able to get a spot at the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:25.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:30.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I fell asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:33.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were probably tried from playing all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:36.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:40.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we have dinner at my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:43.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At Minagi's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:53.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare for my daughter to bring friends home, so I made a special dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:04.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:04.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't asked you your name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:06.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:10.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, your name. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:12.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell me your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:13.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:15.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Comment: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:15.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:18.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:20.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:24.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is... Michiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:27.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:32.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:35.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so your name is Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:41.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually, really, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:48.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:51.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:52.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:54.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a wonderful name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:55.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:59.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter has always loved hamburgers ever since she was little too.
Comment: 0,0:14:59.43,0:14:59.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: more literally 'my daughter' -> 'this girl' but this might be confusing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:06.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She always said that when she got a little sister, she wanted her to eat my hamburgers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:07.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Minagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:08.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.37,0:15:09.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Michiru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:12.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat the hamburgers before they get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:15.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You love them too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:17.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:22.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:24.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are they good?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:26.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they're really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:30.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These hamburgers are my own recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:33.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Comment: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:33.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shorter for timing, just 'here'
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:33.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I taught Minagi how to make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:34.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:39.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll make me very happy if you eat lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:43.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:58.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.59,0:16:00.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:10.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll hold on to this for you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:13.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of it, okay, Minagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:14.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:22.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:24.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:24.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:27.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. She didn't even say goodbye.
Comment: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:27.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: 'without even saying goodbye'
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:27.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:30.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There should still be time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:32.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because the stars aren't out yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:35.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru is probably over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:35.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:39.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:41.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:47.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru, it's not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:51.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous there, so come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:55.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:55.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:17:01.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had so much fun, so I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:06.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a face like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:06.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi, you have to keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:09.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I'll be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:11.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:15.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to be myself thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:20.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you leave, I think I won't ever be able to laugh again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:26.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi, you can laugh with people other than me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:31.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Minagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:31.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito Kunisaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:31.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,let's make a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:33.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:38.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl with wings continues to have sad dreams in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:42.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go back to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:48.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the fun memories you guys gave me back to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.03,0:17:48.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.03,0:17:55.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find her, I want you to tell her many more happy stories,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:59.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and free her from her sad dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:01.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:04.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi, always keep smiling, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:07.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say bye-bye with a smile, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:11.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:14.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say goodbye with a smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:15.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:18.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...because I won't be able to see you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:20.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:21.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because even after you wake up from a dream, the memories will still be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:23.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:30.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Make your memories of me be happy ones, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:33.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is something only you can do.
Comment: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:34.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: Only you can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:36.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:36.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:37.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:42.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you smiling now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:43.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:44.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:45.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:50.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:50.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say bye-bye with a smile for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:52.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you smiling, Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:53.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:55.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sad to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:59.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:00.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm smiling, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:05.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be wonderful if everyone kept smiling all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:08.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The world would be filled with smiles, and everybody would be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:10.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:13.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:14.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:16.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:30.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:43.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:46.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope you're not running away again.
Comment: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:57.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,blah not done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:48.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a rice coupon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:53.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a letter from my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:56.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He is inviting me to come see him during the summer holidays.
Comment: 0,0:19:56.99,0:19:57.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,American check: Vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:20:01.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To my surprise, it seems that I have a little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:05.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He and his current wife had a baby girl.
Comment: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:06.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop current?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:09.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl... Her name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.01,0:20:15.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I was a little hesitant,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:17.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've decided to go meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:20.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother encouraged me to go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:22.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:22.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohno!
Comment: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:25.75,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuma Recycling
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:28.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wings that cannot fly have a use too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:33.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're precious memories of when you once flew in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:42.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't that right, Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:55.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You like bubbles?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:57.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.72,0:20:57.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.72,0:21:00.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, but, I can't blow them very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:03.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then shall I teach you how to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:04.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:07.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:08.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:12.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Minagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:12.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:14.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's, it's...
Comment: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:31.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Koi says 'Um... um...' but that doesn't make sense to me. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:34.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.78,0:21:56.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:56.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Comment: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:57.10,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:21:59.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.95,0:21:59.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.95,0:22:01.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:02.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.85,0:22:05.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Open your eyes, Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.15,0:22:08.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Comment: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:42.05,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.52,0:23:47.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.25,0:23:47.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a coincidence that I started having dreams, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.69,0:23:50.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt that this summer was special.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.89,0:23:53.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to try my best to make a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.39,0:23:56.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I met you and started having those dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.86,0:23:59.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably all connected, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.93,0:23:59.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.93,0:24:05.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make this summer the happiest ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.41,0:24:07.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because it's the summer that I met you, Yukito-san.
